WEBVTT

00:03.046 --> 00:05.548
Fifty years have passed,

00:06.382 --> 00:09.594
but I do not age.

00:12.555 --> 00:15.433
Time has lost it's effect on me.

00:17.560 --> 00:18.811
(EXHALES)

00:19.854 --> 00:21.064
(LAUGHING MANIACALLY)

00:21.147 --> 00:24.234
Yet, the suffering continues.

00:26.277 --> 00:31.574
Aku's grasp chokes the past,
present, and future.

00:32.742 --> 00:35.495
Hope is lost.

00:37.121 --> 00:38.414
Got to get back,

00:38.498 --> 00:39.832
back to the past,

00:40.542 --> 00:41.751
Samurai Jack.

00:41.876 --> 00:44.295
(DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING)

00:54.013 --> 00:56.349
(WIND WHISTLING)

01:02.522 --> 01:03.940
(VEHICLE APPROACHING)

01:05.692 --> 01:06.943
(ENGINE IDLING)

01:07.026 --> 01:08.861
(BLOWS HORN)
(RUMBLING)

01:19.998 --> 01:21.708
(BLOWS HORN)

01:21.791 --> 01:23.167
(RUMBLING)

01:28.464 --> 01:29.674
(SNARLING)

01:29.757 --> 01:30.758
(SNORTING)

01:31.426 --> 01:33.386
(PLAYING BAGPIPES)

01:40.268 --> 01:42.061
(WHEELS SQUEAKING)

01:47.275 --> 01:48.651
(LAUGHING)

01:48.735 --> 01:50.194
We found him!

01:50.278 --> 01:51.821
We're ready, Dad!

01:51.988 --> 01:53.031
What?

01:53.239 --> 01:54.240
Flora!

01:54.324 --> 01:56.618
What in Bonnie blazes are ya' wearing?

01:56.826 --> 02:01.539
I take you out for a day of battle,
and ye dress like you're going dancing.

02:01.956 --> 02:03.499
Cover yourself!

02:03.958 --> 02:06.210
You'll catch your death of cold!

02:06.294 --> 02:07.378
Dad!

02:07.462 --> 02:09.047
That goes for all of you!

02:09.380 --> 02:11.507
ALL: Dad!

02:12.175 --> 02:13.551
Now we...

02:13.968 --> 02:15.970
charge!

02:16.262 --> 02:18.181
(ENGINES ROARING)

02:18.890 --> 02:20.892
(ROARING)

02:24.979 --> 02:27.023
(SCREAMING)

02:27.857 --> 02:29.567
(ALL SCREAMING)

02:45.875 --> 02:48.086
(DISTANT EXPLOSIONS)

02:48.586 --> 02:53.841
Can somebody please stop all that noise!

02:54.300 --> 02:57.970
MAN: I'm sorry, master,
but it seems we are under attack.

02:58.554 --> 03:00.348
Under attack?

03:01.099 --> 03:03.226
Hmm.

03:10.900 --> 03:12.527
(CANNONS FIRING)

03:15.988 --> 03:20.368
Hmm. Perhaps annihilating this scum

03:20.451 --> 03:25.998
will break me out of my malaise.

03:27.041 --> 03:28.626
(SCREAMING)
(FIRING)

03:33.131 --> 03:34.132
What?

03:43.266 --> 03:46.352
You know what? This was a bad idea!

03:46.436 --> 03:47.770
Time to go, girls!

03:47.854 --> 03:48.938
But, Dad...

03:49.105 --> 03:51.065
No arguing! Go!

03:54.026 --> 03:56.195
I'll stall him while you escape.

03:59.198 --> 04:00.992
Meh.

04:01.284 --> 04:02.285
Oh!

04:04.287 --> 04:09.000
Eh, better to make it
a complete annihilation.

04:09.083 --> 04:10.960
(WHEELS SQUEAKING)
SCOTSMAN: Hold it!

04:13.129 --> 04:15.798
You're not going anywhere,
ya' big buffoon!

04:17.884 --> 04:22.305
I'm sorry, old man.
I think you're lost.

04:22.388 --> 04:24.974
I ain't lost, ya tree ogre.

04:25.475 --> 04:27.810
I might be old, but I've lived long enough

04:27.894 --> 04:30.354
to see the world rise
against your tyranny.

04:30.438 --> 04:33.232
Admit it, ya big oaf. You're scared.

04:33.983 --> 04:38.404
The Samurai is still out there
inspiring people by the thousands.

04:38.821 --> 04:41.741
After all these years,
you're powerless against him.

04:42.033 --> 04:45.161
You've been shivering like a wee baby,
hiding in your crib,

04:45.244 --> 04:48.080
afraid to show yourself
'cause ya know he's out there,

04:48.164 --> 04:50.416
and you can't do anything about it.

04:50.625 --> 04:52.126
(LAUGHING)

04:52.210 --> 04:53.920
You're just a big baby!

04:54.003 --> 04:55.838
Why don't you go cry to your mama?

05:00.927 --> 05:03.262
(CLANGING)

05:06.599 --> 05:07.725
No.

05:10.228 --> 05:12.480
(BAGPIPES PLAYING)

05:16.234 --> 05:17.443
Dad.

05:22.573 --> 05:25.576
Ah, why did he bring up the Samurai?

05:25.660 --> 05:26.953
(GROANS)

05:29.455 --> 05:31.666
(FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)

05:40.258 --> 05:42.051
(WIND WHISTLING)

05:45.805 --> 05:48.182
We will avenge you, Father.

05:48.808 --> 05:50.977
(CRYING)
And we will never forget you.

05:56.899 --> 05:58.568
(LAUGHING)

05:58.776 --> 06:01.737
I be back, and in me prime no less!

06:02.071 --> 06:03.072
HEATHER; Dad?

06:03.406 --> 06:05.366
Oh, you live!

06:05.575 --> 06:08.244
Ha! Eh, kind Of...

06:08.661 --> 06:10.037
But how?

06:10.538 --> 06:15.001
Oh, my darling Heather Blossoms.
Celtic magic.

06:17.003 --> 06:18.421
What's next, Father?

06:18.963 --> 06:22.341
We regroup and plan to fight another day.

06:22.550 --> 06:24.260
We'll amass a bigger army.

06:24.427 --> 06:28.973
We'll find Jack,
and finally defeat that big baby.

06:31.309 --> 06:33.519
(INSECTS CHIRPING)

06:46.324 --> 06:48.576
HIGH PRIESTESS:
Aku is the creator of this world

06:48.659 --> 06:49.827
and everything in it.

06:50.494 --> 06:53.164
JACK: Aku is the one
that has ravaged this world.

06:53.581 --> 06:56.918
HIGH PRIESTESS: The Samurai is
the poison killing the land.

06:57.501 --> 07:00.963
JACK: If you let go of your hate,
you will see the truth.

07:05.217 --> 07:07.094
Ashi, what are you doing?

07:07.178 --> 07:08.179
(GASPS)

07:08.262 --> 07:09.972
The Samurai sleeps.

07:10.348 --> 07:13.267
Kill him in his slumber before he wakes.

07:14.268 --> 07:15.311
No.

07:15.519 --> 07:16.896
I have questions, Mother.

07:17.688 --> 07:20.232
The Samurai, he saved my life.

07:20.316 --> 07:22.360
- He--
- How dare you?

07:22.735 --> 07:24.528
You know he is deceitful.

07:24.779 --> 07:28.157
He will do everything in his power
to defy the master.

07:28.532 --> 07:32.995
You were always the weak one,
distracted, unfocused.

07:33.537 --> 07:35.790
May Aku punish you for your sins.

07:36.415 --> 07:38.167
I just want the truth.

07:38.751 --> 07:41.295
You have failed us.

07:42.713 --> 07:44.090
(FOOTSTEPS RUNNING)
(GASPS)

07:44.173 --> 07:45.383
(SPLASHING)

07:57.937 --> 07:59.689
(ROARING)

08:03.359 --> 08:04.402
Get on.

08:12.952 --> 08:15.162
(PEPPY MUSIC PLAYING)

08:20.418 --> 08:21.711
(DOLPHINS CHITTERING)

08:31.387 --> 08:33.014
(ROARING)
Hold on.

09:02.793 --> 09:05.004
(BIRDS SQUAWKING)

09:05.254 --> 09:06.547
Thank you, friend.

09:06.797 --> 09:08.716
I shall not forget your kindness.

09:10.426 --> 09:12.219
(ROARS)

09:23.981 --> 09:25.024
Good bye.

09:29.570 --> 09:31.697
(INSECTS CHIRPING)

09:43.209 --> 09:44.668
(PEOPLE SCREAMING)

09:45.461 --> 09:48.047
Please, no more, please.

09:50.299 --> 09:51.300
(SCREAMING STOPS)

09:52.218 --> 09:53.469
What do you want?

09:53.803 --> 09:54.804
The truth.

09:56.013 --> 09:57.681
I have already told you the truth.

09:58.015 --> 09:59.100
Show me.

10:01.268 --> 10:02.269
No.

10:02.353 --> 10:04.897
No? What do you mean, no?

10:05.106 --> 10:07.691
You tell me that
everything that I know is wrong,

10:07.775 --> 10:09.485
but refuse to prove any of it.

10:09.777 --> 10:13.155
You're afraid,
afraid that I will see you're a liar!

10:14.406 --> 10:18.244
You are too blinded by Aku's hate.
You won't change.

10:18.953 --> 10:20.496
What do you know of me,

10:20.579 --> 10:23.999
everything I have endured
up until this moment?

10:24.250 --> 10:26.001
You know nothing, Samurai.

10:26.335 --> 10:28.754
You are just a lowly, soulless pig.

10:28.838 --> 10:30.005
JACK: Very well.

10:30.506 --> 10:31.715
I will show you.

10:35.469 --> 10:36.470
Please sit.

10:43.727 --> 10:45.437
Well, when do we start?

10:45.771 --> 10:47.690
In the morning. Have patience.

10:48.149 --> 10:49.150
(GROANS)

10:57.199 --> 10:59.702
Samurai, the stars.

11:00.202 --> 11:02.496
They are Aku's creation, yes?

11:02.830 --> 11:04.248
You th... No!

11:04.832 --> 11:05.833
Then who?

11:06.667 --> 11:10.504
When I was very young,
my mother told me a story

11:10.588 --> 11:13.382
of when all the Earth
was covered in darkness.

11:14.216 --> 11:18.929
But a little magical boy named "sun"
and his little sister named "moon"

11:19.013 --> 11:21.974
rode a Phoenix up into the darkness.

11:23.893 --> 11:25.936
They shot enchanted arrows

11:27.354 --> 11:33.194
that exploded and filled the dark sky
with an infinity of stars.

11:34.904 --> 11:36.530
(PHOENIX CRIES)

11:46.415 --> 11:48.542
(BIRDS CHIRPING)

11:49.585 --> 11:50.586
(GASPS)

11:56.717 --> 11:57.885
That tree...

11:58.135 --> 11:59.220
One of many.

11:59.929 --> 12:03.224
The trees stretched
as far as the eye can see.

12:05.893 --> 12:11.607
It was a testament to nature's wonder
until Aku destroyed everything.

12:11.941 --> 12:16.487
He left but one,
a reminder of his power and oppression.

12:16.654 --> 12:17.655
Why?

12:17.738 --> 12:19.823
Aku is evil personified.

12:20.074 --> 12:22.034
The darkest soul from the pit of hate.

12:22.701 --> 12:27.122
To him, all that is good
and innocent must be decimated.

12:27.331 --> 12:29.792
That is his will, his desire.

12:30.000 --> 12:31.835
Here is your truth.

12:34.797 --> 12:38.676
A city of Aku, a gateway to evil.

12:39.635 --> 12:40.803
(DISTANT EXPLOSION)

12:44.848 --> 12:46.058
Come quickly!

12:46.892 --> 12:50.354
My friend, trust me.
It is a thing of beauty on you.

12:50.688 --> 12:54.108
Fresh shoes, freshly made every day.

12:54.316 --> 12:56.151
Vintage, period coats,

12:56.235 --> 12:58.404
16th, 17th, 18th centuries.

12:58.487 --> 13:00.197
(ELEVATOR WHIRS)

13:03.492 --> 13:05.327
(RUMBLING)
There.

13:10.833 --> 13:13.544
(OMINOUS INSTRUMENTAL MUSIC PLAYING)

13:22.636 --> 13:26.432
We are criminal banished from our world.

13:26.515 --> 13:31.687
We hear that Aku welcomes
those that are like us.

13:31.854 --> 13:33.897
Most enthusiastically.

13:35.065 --> 13:38.360
Your new home will be coordinates 6-12-71.

13:38.444 --> 13:40.029
(CHILDREN LAUGHING)

13:42.448 --> 13:44.658
It is occupied.

13:45.034 --> 13:47.578
(SCOFFS) Is that a problem for you?

13:50.706 --> 13:54.585
No. No problem.

13:55.127 --> 13:58.005
The innocent and weak always preyed upon.

14:01.842 --> 14:03.135
Catastrophe.

14:05.346 --> 14:06.680
Devastation.

14:09.767 --> 14:10.976
Carnage.

14:14.021 --> 14:15.105
Enough.

14:15.189 --> 14:16.607
I've seen enough.

14:16.982 --> 14:18.233
Do you believe now?

14:20.277 --> 14:22.404
Yes. What can we do?

14:23.072 --> 14:24.490
- Nothing.
- What?

14:24.573 --> 14:27.618
What do you mean, nothing?
We have to do something.

14:27.910 --> 14:31.330
I've fought Aku for ages.
I've seen countless innocents die.

14:32.247 --> 14:35.209
I've lived this nightmare
for what seems like an eternity.

14:35.751 --> 14:37.252
There is no way to defeat him.

14:38.462 --> 14:41.423
There is no hope. No way out.

14:43.050 --> 14:44.385
MAN: Help.

14:46.053 --> 14:47.054
Help.

14:50.265 --> 14:52.684
(BOARDS CLATTERING)

14:53.185 --> 14:54.436
(GROANS)

14:58.607 --> 15:03.028
You've come back at last, Samurai Jack.

15:03.946 --> 15:05.197
You've come.

15:06.949 --> 15:08.033
What happened?

15:08.283 --> 15:11.036
(COUGHING)

15:13.330 --> 15:17.376
They, they took all the children.

15:17.584 --> 15:18.585
(GASPS)

15:18.669 --> 15:21.130
- Where?
- The factory.

15:34.893 --> 15:37.146
(ALARM BLARING)

15:39.148 --> 15:42.401
(MACHINERY WHIRRING)

15:54.997 --> 15:56.206
(BEEPING)

15:56.290 --> 15:57.458
Do you hear that?

15:57.541 --> 15:59.293
- No. Run.
- What?

16:00.210 --> 16:02.754
(GROWLING, ROARING)

16:04.381 --> 16:05.424
Run!

16:09.636 --> 16:11.680
(HIGH-PITCHED HUMMING)

16:11.763 --> 16:15.350
Something has to be
controlling them. That sound!

16:15.434 --> 16:17.603
(GROWLING, SNARLING)

16:18.854 --> 16:19.938
Destroy the source!

17:13.575 --> 17:15.202
(MACHINERY POWERS ON)

17:33.470 --> 17:35.847
(GRUNTING)

17:38.725 --> 17:41.895
(MECHANICAL FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)

17:44.106 --> 17:48.443
(CHUCKLES) Well, what do we have here?

17:48.819 --> 17:51.530
A little Samurai sympathizer.

17:51.989 --> 17:54.283
And quite the pretty one.

17:55.158 --> 17:58.036
(LAUGHS CREEPILY)

18:01.039 --> 18:02.916
(ELECTRICITY CRACKLING)

18:04.751 --> 18:06.503
(SCREAMING)

18:06.837 --> 18:08.255
(GRUNTING)

18:08.422 --> 18:10.674
(SNARLING, GROWLING)

18:22.603 --> 18:25.105
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

18:26.607 --> 18:28.609
(GROWLING)

18:30.986 --> 18:32.279
(GROWLING, ROARING)

18:40.912 --> 18:42.497
(YELLS)

18:47.419 --> 18:50.380
(ELECTRICITY CRACKLING)
(SCREAMING)

18:50.797 --> 18:52.132
(GROANS)

18:53.258 --> 18:55.844
Sorry, Princess. Ran out of juice.

18:56.261 --> 18:57.429
No worries, though.

18:57.763 --> 19:00.349
A quick re-charge
and then back to the fun.

19:05.228 --> 19:07.856
(SINGING INDISTINCTLY)

19:15.405 --> 19:18.825
(LAUGHING) Would you look at that.

19:20.827 --> 19:22.579
(SOLEMN INSTRUMENTAL MUSIC PLAYING)

19:22.663 --> 19:23.955
Righteous fool.

19:24.039 --> 19:26.750
After everything,
he still can't hurt an innocent.

19:27.042 --> 19:30.921
Turning those little brats into weapons,
pretty ingenious, right?

19:31.004 --> 19:34.341
(CHUCKLES)
Children are foolish little things,

19:34.633 --> 19:36.301
easily manipulated.

19:36.385 --> 19:38.345
Surgically implant a chip in their neck,

19:38.553 --> 19:40.722
and the right audio frequency
does the rest.

19:41.181 --> 19:44.101
(ELECTRICITY CRACKLES)
Well, back to the fun.

19:44.476 --> 19:46.436
(SCREAMING)

19:50.273 --> 19:51.983
(GROANS)

19:53.110 --> 19:54.486
What the...

19:55.237 --> 19:56.822
(SCREAMING)

19:59.282 --> 20:00.283
(GRUNTS)

20:06.456 --> 20:08.041
Oh, no, you don't!

20:10.544 --> 20:11.545
(GRUNTS)

20:12.629 --> 20:15.340
(ELECTRICITY CRACKLING)
(SCREAMING)

20:24.516 --> 20:26.351
(GRUNTING)

20:26.435 --> 20:28.228
(GROANING)

20:33.275 --> 20:35.318
(SNARLING, GROWLING)

20:35.986 --> 20:37.028
(YELLS)

20:39.072 --> 20:40.240
(HIGH-PITCHED BEEPING)

20:40.323 --> 20:41.450
(SCREAMING)

20:41.533 --> 20:42.576
(GASPS)

20:47.497 --> 20:48.623
(ELECTRICITY CRACKLING)

20:50.625 --> 20:51.877
No!

20:52.794 --> 20:54.880
(SHOUTS) No!

21:00.677 --> 21:03.388
(HORSE NEIGHING)

21:03.722 --> 21:05.515
It is time.

21:13.523 --> 21:14.524
Yes.

21:23.992 --> 21:26.244
ASHI: Samurai! Samurai?

21:27.245 --> 21:28.455
(GASPS)

21:37.506 --> 21:40.175
(WHIMPERING)

21:44.471 --> 21:46.640
We did it. Samurai!

21:47.390 --> 21:49.351
Samurai? Samurai?

21:51.102 --> 21:53.438
(SHOUTS) Samurai Jack!

21:53.814 --> 21:54.815
♪ <i>Watch out</i>

21:54.898 --> 21:55.899
♪ <i>Gotta get back</i>

21:55.982 --> 21:56.983
♪ <i>Back to the past</i>

21:57.067 --> 21:58.235
♪ <i>Samurai Jack</i>

21:58.318 --> 21:59.694
♪ <i>Watch out</i> ♪

22:03.573 --> 22:04.658
♪ <i>Gotta be back</i>

22:04.741 --> 22:05.742
♪ <i>Back to the past</i>

22:05.826 --> 22:07.118
♪ <i>Samurai Jack</i>

22:07.577 --> 22:08.578
♪ <i>Watch out</i>

22:11.623 --> 22:13.834
♪ <i>Jack, Jack, Jack, Jack, Jack</i>

22:17.212 --> 22:18.213
♪ <i>Watch out</i>

22:18.296 --> 22:19.422
♪ <i>Gotta be back</i>

22:20.382 --> 22:21.675
♪ <i>Samurai Jack</i>

22:21.758 --> 22:23.051
♪ <i>Watch out</i> ♪
